com.yworks.yfiles.view

Class PointSelectionIndicatorInstaller

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.yworks.yfiles.view.PointSelectionIndicatorInstaller
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ICanvasObjectInstaller, ISelectionIndicatorInstaller

    public class PointSelectionIndicatorInstaller
extends Object
implements ISelectionIndicatorInstaller
    A simple ISelectionIndicatorInstaller implementation that draws an ellipse centered at a given point in world coordinate space.
